{
  "texts": [
    "A new object classification architecture is introduced in [36] by combining Capsule Network and a Self-Attention strategy.",
    "A shallow CapsNet network with self-attention help is used instead of the deeper network to extract important features with low computational complexity.",
    "Self-attention strategy obtained a better accuracy with the easy train when dealing with fewer data samples and images with complicated backgrounds since it can help the network to focus on more significant portions of the image.",
    "However, more investigation of both the convolution neural network and the attention needs to be implemented to achieve better accuracy.",
    "The proposed algorithmThis paper is motivated by the potential to enhance scene classification performance in remote sensing by employing two types of networks."
  ]
}